            "type": "paragraph",
            "html": "Simply add a new object to <code>pages.json</code> with the required properties:"
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
            "language": "json",
            "code": "{\n  \"id\": \"contact\",\n  \"type\": \"main\",\n  \"path\": \"/contact\",\n  \"title\": \"Contact\",\n  \"pageTitle\": \"Contact - Simple SPA\",\n  \"icon\": \"üìß\",\n  \"content\": {\n    \"heading\": \"Contact Us\",\n    \"sections\": [\n      {\n        \"type\": \"paragraph\",\n        \"text\": \"Get in touch with us!\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 2,
            "text": "Deep Linking on Cloudflare"
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "html": "Deep linking is enabled through a <code>_redirects</code> file that tells Cloudflare to serve <code>index.html</code> for all routes. The JavaScript router then handles the actual routing on the client side."
